Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.95,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:32.37,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:32.37,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:36.83,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:36.83,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:43.13,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾いた風に抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:43.13,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎面吹着干燥的风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:49.60,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命への 真偽を覚え 刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:49.60,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂得了生命的真伪 铭刻于心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:53.02,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ただ 傍に居たいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:53.02,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 祈愿待在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:55.60,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人を愛し 人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:55.60,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱过 恨过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:59.11,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲しさは  優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:59.11,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲伤最后化作温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:04.07,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}例え光が 消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:04.07,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算陷入无尽黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.07,0:01:08.82,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.07,0:01:08.82,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍会寻觅明日希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:13.12,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃えた血の呼吸 消え寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:13.12,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃烧的血液 停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:18.21,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:18.21,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果之缘 最终转化成奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:20.42,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:20.42,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:22.88,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:22.88,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:26.63,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闇を搔き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:26.63,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拨开黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:30.43,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手を伸ばすよ どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:30.43,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伸手向前 追寻你到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:32.72,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:32.72,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.72,0:01:36.35,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか 変えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.72,0:01:36.35,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总有一天 命运将会转变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:41.02,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}涙の意味 無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:41.02,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要让眼泪白流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:45.65,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}螺旋のように 蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:45.65,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如螺旋一般交织骚动的尽头
